---
title: Crispy Chicken & Bacon Alfredo with Spinach, Parmesan & Chives
description: Our chefs channeled their inner alfredo lover in tonight’s meal and took it to the next level with not just one, but two decadent proteins: crispy chicken and bacon. Both are served with al dente spaghetti that gets tossed in a homemade creamy alfredo sauce with chives and spinach. Don’t be al-fred-o to lick up any sauce left on the plate...
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/621e8a0b169e5a19621e697c-94a49c1d.jpg
